        <TD VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH=693 HEIGHT=133 COLSPAN=3>
                    
                      <div align="left">
                      <table border="0" width="696" height="136">
                        <tr><td width='686' height='19' valign='top' align='left'> <font face='Arial,sans-serif' SIZE=2 COLOR=#ffff80> 2001-02-05 - Test Server Updates</font> </td></tr><tr><td width='686' height='19'></td></tr><tr><td width='686' height='19' valign='top' align='left'> <font face='Arial,sans-serif' SIZE=2 COLOR=#C0C0C0> p><span class="newstext">These are the latest patch message from off of the Test Server:
<ul>
 February 2nd, 7:00pm<br>
 -------------------------<br>
 1) Superior Healing moved to level 51 for shamans and druids. casting difficulty reduced<br>
 2) New level 55 Druid and shaman spell, Chloroblast, similar to remedy for clerics.<br>
 3) New Druid spell at level 60, upgrade to superior healing, Natures Touch.<br>
 4) Paladins:<br>
 a) Add Endure Magic spell at level 30<br>
 b) Add Resist Magic at 55<br>
 c) Move Guard spell from 49 to 39<br>
 d) Move Armor of Faith from 53 to 49<br>
 e) New level 53 paladin spell, Divine Glory, clone of divine strength but 100 hp instead of 200<br>
 f) New level 59 spell, Celestial Cleansing 110 hp healdot per tick, for 4 ticks. 1.5 second casting time. Recast time 30 secs.<br>
 g) Defense skill cap made exactly same as warriors<br>
 5) Shadowknights:<br>
 a) Remove artificially inflated mana cost for pre level 50 lifetap spells<br>
 b) Move Spirit Tap to level 55<br>
 c) Move Drain Spirit to level 57<br>
 d) Add Drain Soul at level 60<br>
 e) Grim Aura added at level 22<br>
 f) Move Shieldskin to level 34<br>
 g) Mini Intensify Death pet buff added at 29, 10% (min) haste 5 str 5 ac<br>
 h) Add Diamondskin spell at 59<br>
 i) Defense skill cap made exactly same as warriors<br>
 6) Rangers:<br>
 a) Add Endure Cold at 22<br>
 b) Add Skin Like Nature at 59<br>
 c) Add FireFist at 22<br>
 d) Move Bramblecoat from 49 to 39<br>
 e) Add Spikecoat at 49<br>
 f) Add resist cold at 55<br>
 g) Add Panic Animal at 22<br>
 i) Offense and weapons skill made identical to warriors<br>
 7) Bards:<br>
 a) Cassindra`s Chant of Clarity for Bards at level 20<br>
 b) Bards defensive skill made exactly the same as a warriors<br>
 <br>
 8) Magicians<br>
 a) New level 59 spell, Valiant Companion, makes pet immune to fear (own pet only)<br>
 b) New level 39 spell, Summon Companion, if pet not noticed by any hostile npcs, pet returns to you instantly.<br>
 c) Rain spells no longer count pets against total number of entities they can damage (all rain spells)<br>
 d) Expedience for Mages at level 29. Target casters pet, J Boot speed buff for pet only<br>
 <br>
 9) Warriors<br>
 a) Aggressive and Defensive disciplines fixed before they would only affect damage taken and not affect damage dealt out. Now they affect both as
 designed.<br>
 <br>
 10) New Scrolls are temporarily available in East Commons
</ul>
</span>
<p><br>
